 n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League, trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Everton.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Klopp v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng s\u1ebd b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, v\u00ec sao ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m th\u1ebf? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i 5 ph\u00fat r\u1eb1ng Salah \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi Liverpool, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u1edd xem (li\u1ec7u Salah c\u00f3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c hay kh\u00f4ng).&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn Man City\" title=\"Salah Liverpool vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Tran-dau-Liverpool-vs-Man-City-Bo-mat-la-thuong-cua-Lu-doan-do-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn trong 60-70 ph\u00fat, sau \u0111\u00f3 Everton \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mong mu\u1ed1n&rdquo; &ndash; Klopp n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfp. &ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n 1A, nh\u01b0ng 1B c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 quan tr\u1ecdng khi gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Man City&rdquo; &ndash; Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua Man xanh v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 b\u00e0n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265747\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/07/highlight-everton-vs-liverpool-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-vs-liverpool-man-chay-da-khong-te-truoc-dai-chien-172-183746.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/everton-vs-liverpool-man-chay-da-khong-te-truoc-dai-chien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-vs-liverpool-man-chay-da-khong-te-truoc-dai-chien-172-183746.html\">Everton vs Liverpool: M\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span><br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a, v\u00e0 Klopp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u1eefa Everton vs Liverpool.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div