.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn derby Real vs Atletico di\u1ec5n ra th\u1eadt \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zinedine Zidane. H\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Juventus 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi-184-183504.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo</strong></span> \u0111ang h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n qua, trong khi Los Blancos \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Juventus 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League th\u00ec Cristiano Ronaldo l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u201cng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n\u201d n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eadt d\u1eady t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng. Gianluigi Buffon th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ng\u1ea3 m\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran derby Real vs Atletico 21h15 ngay 84 vong 31 La Liga hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn derby Real vs Atletico 21h15 ng\u00e0y 84 v\u00f2ng 31 La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Tran-derby-Real-vs-Atletico-21h15-ngay-84-vong-31-La-Liga-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Real Madrid m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng trong 12 tr\u1eadn cho Real t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo ghi t\u1edbi 24 b\u00e0n \u0111i k\u00e8m 5 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u0169ng trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia ch\u01a1i 14 tr\u1eadn, th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 12, h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Champions League, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang-184-183492.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</strong></span> trong khi t\u1ea1i La Liga h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong t\u1ed1p 4. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i m\u1edbi gi\u00fap Los Blancos ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus c\u00f2n Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m xem \u0111i xem l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn derby Real vs Atletico v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n t\u1ed1i \u0111a. X\u00e9t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m kh\u00f3 \u01b0a. V\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Real \u0111ang ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. V\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nacho, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid Isco di bong\" title=\"Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid Isco di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Atletico-Madrid-vs-Real-Madrid-Isco-di-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Isco v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn derby Real vs Atletico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Zidane t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Real. Ngo\u00e0i Ronaldo th\u0103ng hoa t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec9nh, nh\u1eefng Karim Benzema v\u00e0 Gareth Bale c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng Lucas Vazquez v\u00e0 Marco Asensio c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m tr\u00f2n vai m\u1ed7i khi ra s\u00e2n, g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u201cSi\u00eau d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb\u201d Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 James Rodriguez m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nIsco v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus cho th\u1ea5y anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Real d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t. HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch \u0111a d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau, trong nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang-184-183492.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang-184-183492.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid: Gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n n\u00e0o cho K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng?</span><br>\r\n<span>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vui v\u1ebb ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t khi khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Real vs Atletico. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 xoay tua, nh\u1eefng Vazquez, Asensio, Kovacic r\u1ed3i Bale c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean kia, Atletico \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y run r\u1ea9y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Real. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 3 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc 8 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. So v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m, nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Atletico th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Real Madrid vs Atletico\" title=\"Preview Real Madrid vs Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-ngay-hom-nay-842018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn derby Real vs Atletico 21h15 ng\u00e0y 8/4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i La Liga, Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u thua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Atletico c\u00f2n c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111i xa, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Real vs Atletico. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Atletico c\u0169ng \u201cch\u1ec9\u201d th\u1eafng Sporting Lisbon 2-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Europa League. Trong \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 6 tu\u1ea7n sau tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEuropa League l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Atletico c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 n\u00e0y. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid tranh \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 3 hay th\u1ee9 4. V\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, Real s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nReal Madrid (4-3-1-2): </strong>1.Navas; 2.Carvajal, 4.Ramos, 5.Varane, 12.Marcelo; 10.Modric, 8.Kroos, 14.Casemiro, 22.Isco; 7.Ronaldo, 11.Bale.<br>\r\n<strong>Atletico Madrid (4-2-3-1):</strong> 13.Oblak; 20.Juanfran, 15.Savic, 2.Godin, 19.Hernandez; 14.Gabi, 5.Partey; 6.Koke, 7.Griezmann, 8.Niguez; 18.Costa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Real th\u1eafng 3-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Real Madrid vs Atletico\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Real-Madrid-vs-Atletico-(4-3-3-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-zidane-tu-tin-ve-kha-nang-giu-chan-gareth-bale-180-183743.html\">HLV Zidane t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-barca-khong-mua-verratti-180-183658.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-modric-se-roi-real-madrid-o-he-2018-180-183636.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Modric s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi-184-183504.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ronaldo h\u00f3a \u201cTh\u00e1nh\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Messi</span></di