00_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c sau tr\u1eadn derby Man City 2-3 MU, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Manchester City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 vua n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Etihad k\u1ebft th\u00fac sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, Manchester United phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u201cvua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng\u201d tr\u1ee9 danh \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3n linh \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m \u1ed3n \u00e0o m\u1edf h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh trong 98 gi\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba r\u1ed3i pha \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Chris Smalling \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola ngay t\u1ea1i Etihad trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, ng\u00e0y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nhu\u1ed9m xanh Manchester v\u00e0 to\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep sau tran Man City 2-3 MU Hom nay don gian la ngay cua MU hinh anh\" title=\"Pep sau tr\u1eadn Man City 2-3 MU H\u00f4m nay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/pep-guardiola-hom-nay-don-gian-la-ngay-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn Man City 2-3 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau tr\u1eadn derby si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Man City 2-3 MU, h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u nh\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Pep: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 10-15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Man Utd.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cNh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ra n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t penalty trong c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p hai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u01a1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac qu\u00ean \u0111i, \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.\u201d \u2013 Pep l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111ang xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ecd c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n sau, khi ba b\u00e0n thua tr\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t ch\u01b0a ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 san b\u1eb1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Man City vs Man Utd\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Man Utd\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/013256-Thong-tin-sau-tran-Man-City-vs-Man-Utd.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City 2-3 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHighlights tr\u1eadn Man City 2-3 MU:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"cent